âŸ£âŸª *Usá´‡Ê€É´á´€á´á´‡:* âŸ«âŸ¢
    ${nickname}


âŸ£âŸª *Dá´‡sá´„Ê€Éªá´˜á´›Éªá´É´:* âŸ«âŸ¢
    ${description}
    
 _Cara simpan digalery:\n1. Download dulu videonya\n2. Buka terus klik titik 3 pojok kanan atas\n3. lalu klik simpan!_

*Â©ã€Œ ð–ðšð§ð§ðð¨ð­ð³-ðŒðƒ ã€*
`.trim(), m)
}
handler.help = ['tiktok'].map(v => v + ' <url>')
handler.tags = ['downloader']
handler.command = /^(tiktok|tt|ttdl|tiktokdl)$/i

export default handler